                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1997-12-03</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book has every catigory of coffee beverage and is great for the beginner, or as a gift for the friend who just bought there first cappuccino/expresso machine.  I found lots of interesting drinks to try, hot and cold as well as lists and ideas for flavors to go with the drinks.  I brought it home and read it, then tried several items all that same night.</span>
                  
              
